---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SchemaMarkup from '../../components/SchemaMarkup.astro';

const draft = false;
const publishDate = "April 1, 2026";
const author = "The Valley Clean Team";
const readTime = "7 min read";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Why Our Provider-First Model Matters for Your Home"
  description="Discover why The Valley Clean Team chooses to pay our cleaning providers more. Learn how our 50/50 split ensures a higher quality clean for your family."
>
  <SchemaMarkup
    type="article"
    title="Why Our Provider-First Model Matters for Your Home"
    description="Discover why The Valley Clean Team chooses to pay our cleaning providers more. Learn how our 50/50 split ensures a higher quality clean for your family."
    publishDate={publishDate}
    author={author}
  />
  

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-900 via-gray-800 to-teal-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-teal-500/20 text-teal-400 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          The Secret Sauce
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          Why Our Provider-First<br>
          <span class="text-teal-400">Model Matters</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 text-gray-400 mb-8">
          <span>{publishDate}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{readTime}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>By {author}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <article class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700">

        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-8">
          The dirty secret of the cleaning industry? Most companies treat their staff like a commodity. The industry standard pay for a residential cleaner is often around $10 to $12 an hour. But cleaning is **hard work**. It's physically demanding, it's meticulous, and it requires a high level of trust to enter a stranger's home.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          At The Valley Clean Team, we took everything we hated about the corporate world and inverted it. We call it our **Provider-First Model**.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">The 50/50 Split</h2>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          We don't pay hourly. We do a 50/50 split. When you book a clean with us, half of that revenue goes directly to the professional in your home. This means our providers consistently earn more than we do as owners after we pay for marketing, insurance, and software.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          Why did we choose this? Because we believe that **if you take care of the people, the business takes care of itself.** Most cleaning companies deal with constant turnover and "no-shows" because their staff doesn't feel valued. Our providers are partners. They are invested in the success of every clean because they are treated like the professionals they are.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Why This Matters For You (The Homeowner)</h2>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          You might wonder: "Why does it matter what the cleaner gets paid as long as my floors are shining?" It matters because **you can’t teach someone to care.**
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          When a provider feels valued, respected, and fairly compensated, they don't just "show up." They take ownership of your home. They notice the dust on the baseboard. They make sure the mirrors are streak-free. They treat your home with the same respect they give their own.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          When you book with us, you aren't just getting a clean home — you're supporting a local economy where hard work is actually rewarded. You're ensuring that the person in your home is happy to be there, motivated to do their best work, and committed to your satisfaction.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">A Different Kind of Cleaning Company</h2>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          We aren't just about sparkling counters and clean floors. We're about building a community of excellence. By putting our providers first, we create a ripple effect of quality that reaches every corner of your home.
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8 space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-600">
          <li><strong>Same Team Every Visit:</strong> Because our providers stay with us, you get the same friendly faces who know your home's unique needs.</li>
          <li><strong>Higher Standards:</strong> Our providers are incentivized to go above and beyond because they are true partners in the business.</li>
          <li><strong>Peace of Mind:</strong> Knowing that your home is being cared for by someone who is fairly compensated and truly valued.</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          Experience the difference that caring makes. Let us show you what a "Provider-First" clean looks like.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500 to-teal-400 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
        Ready for a Truly Professional Clean?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto opacity-90">
        Support a business that values its people. Book your first clean with The Valley Clean Team today and feel the difference.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-gray-900 text-white font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors text-lg">
          Get a Free Quote
        </a>
        <a href="tel:256-826-1100" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-teal-600 font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors text-lg">
          Call 256-826-1100
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
